{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO838901B1906P1D1N002667", "chronotag": "1762557557781", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "I-2667", "numeroOrdreDepot": "2667", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "AN", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO838901B1906P1D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PRJLANR5L17B1906", "triAmendement": "jfaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaae", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA643104", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845425", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"acteurRef": ["PA793094", "PA266797"]}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "Mme&#160;Minard,  M.&#160;Ray et M.&#160;Gosselin"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "ARTICLE 33", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. 33", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE 33", "type": "ARTICLE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/1906A.asp#D_ARTICLE_33"}, "amendementStandard": {"alinea": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositif": "<p>Supprimer cet article.&nbsp;</p>", "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Cet amendement tend &#x00E0;&nbsp;supprimer le m&#x00E9;canisme d&#x2019;&#x00E9;cr&#x00EA;tement du FCTVA, introduit pour ma&#x00EE;triser la d&#x00E9;pense publique, mais devenu aujourd&#x2019;hui un frein direct &#x00E0; l&#x2019;investissement local.</p><p><br>L&#x2019;&#x00E9;cr&#x00EA;tement consiste &#x00E0; r&#x00E9;duire le montant du remboursement de TVA lorsque l&#x2019;investissement des collectivit&#x00E9;s d&#x00E9;passe un certain seuil. Ce m&#x00E9;canisme p&#x00E8;se principalement sur les communes et intercommunalit&#x00E9;s les plus dynamiques, qui r&#x00E9;alisent des projets structurants dans les domaines de la transition &#x00E9;cologique, de l&#x2019;habitat ou des mobilit&#x00E9;s.</p><p><br>En limitant la compensation de TVA, il fragilise les capacit&#x00E9;s d&#x2019;autofinancement et&nbsp;ralentit la mise en &#x0153;uvre des politiques publiques locales, alors m&#x00EA;me que l&#x2019;&#x00C9;tat appelle &#x00E0; une acc&#x00E9;l&#x00E9;ration des investissements de transition.</p><p><br>Sa suppression contribuerait &#x00E0;&nbsp;restaurer la pleine efficacit&#x00E9; du FCTVA&nbsp;et &#x00E0; redonner de la lisibilit&#x00E9; et de la confiance aux acteurs locaux dans leurs d&#x00E9;cisions d&#x2019;investissement.</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2025-10-22", "datePublication": "2025-10-23", "soumisArticle40": "false", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "AC", "libelle": "A discuter"}, "sousEtat": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "dateSort": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "sort": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO838901B1906P1D1N002667?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionCommune": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionIdentique": {"idDiscussion": "83459", "typePosition": "Milieu"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}